Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.00,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要哭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.79,0:00:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.36,0:00:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.06,0:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看起来岂不像是我在单方面地欺负后辈吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.38,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想哭的是我才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.50,0:00:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但被妹妹敬而远之 而且连个理由都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不对我诉说呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.36,0:00:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说我就只是这种程度的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 成为姐妹又有什么意义呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.20,0:00:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要接受念珠呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.53,0:00:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另找一天心平气和地再谈谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也稍微有点过于激动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.61,0:01:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能说得也太过份了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.01,0:01:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.29,0:01:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？ 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.83,0:01:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始商议明天活动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.27,0:01:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.27,0:01:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.17,0:01:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也想单方面地将我当成坏人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.75,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.09,0:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.71,0:01:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越与身同高的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.08,0:01:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.69,0:01:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让裙子的摺痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.57,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让白色的水手服领结外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.71,0:02:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒缓的行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.61,0:02:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.27,0:03:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}吃惊的巧克力·后篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是四季常开呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概被姐姐讨厌了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想你或许愿意自已一个人待着 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.63,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说起来 刚才真像是过去情景的重现啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.93,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳与祥子有时真是相似得让人吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.00,0:04:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的佑巳与祥子\N就像是一年又十个月以前的祥子与蓉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是现在的红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.41,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子因为成长环境的原因 所以不大擅长表达自已的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.13,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常因闷得慌而发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祥子大人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子对她训斥道“你这样我什么都无法明白”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“有想说的话就清楚地说出来”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.82,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你内心深处的话语为什么就不能向我倾诉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话我什么都无法明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被蓉子那样训斥后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子也像是忍耐到了极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后就渐渐变得能表达自已的意见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.50,0:05:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 这大概就是祥子对佑巳感到焦躁不安的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦躁不安？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为看到佑巳就像是看到了自已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子她的本性并未改变啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也一定是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才焦躁不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.27,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在佑巳的身上\N看到了自已身上也有的讨厌部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以原谅祥子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.74,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 不要因为这点事就变得讨厌祥子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这个温室 稍微有点过敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人很快就要毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后我该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再没有能像这样来帮助我的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是说了些让人开心的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能再多向祥子诉说一些真心话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衹要至少能做到一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么事一定都能顺利地渡过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 向佑巳布置一道作业题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.83,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭自已的力量与祥子重归于好 好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～ 佑巳不送我巧克力吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.24,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向志摩子同学说声“给我巧克力”不就好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么只有放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.96,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不给我巧克力的话 我就吃掉佑巳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边是祥子大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.47,0:07:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败品就留作用情不专的白蔷薇大人的惩罚用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先必须对昨天的事道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 将祥子大人叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佑巳同学啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.59,0:08:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学也许把卡片藏在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再胡闹了 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉我卡片藏在哪里也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只听一下我的预测好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.93,0:08:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 来得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 能否把这个吵人家伙带出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是小气鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.12,0:08:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学 请稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 昨天真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.99,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 如果方便的话 今天能给我一点时间吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想继续昨天的话题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻宝结束后如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我在温室等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温室？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 那么就在温室见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢大家的勇跃参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.63,0:09:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我说明一下活动规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.90,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要找的就是这些卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.75,0:09:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红 白 黄的卡片将分别藏在校内的某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制时间是一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到卡片后 请带回到作为本部的蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.18,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着就可获赠\N作为附加奖的与花蕾们的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.28,0:10:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请花蕾的姐妹们到前面来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.60,0:10:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了公平起见 请花蕾的姐妹们迟五分钟开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！ 怎么这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在活动结束前 花蕾们请来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到黄蔷薇大人竟然也会参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没理由白白放过这么有趣的活动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.16,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我一定会找到红色的卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 稍微招呼一下客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.22,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 方便的话能否进来谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有花蕾们在哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.66,0:11:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人不想去找志摩子同学的卡片吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你说是志摩子的卡片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 关于隐藏的地点我是一点头绪也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.72,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 明明志摩子同学的卡片大概就在那里的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说那个房间里藏着什么好东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 已过了5分钟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待着佑巳的英勇奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.64,0:11:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.31,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊 志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟白蔷薇大人约会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.78,0:11:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人既没参加什么俱乐部活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没加入什么委员会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是在蔷薇馆里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是祥子大人的FAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概以为我知道卡片藏在哪里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.14,0:12:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～ 现在可不是玩捉迷藏的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 还有十五分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人的红色卡片到底在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我要藏的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的话 一定会藏在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 好像吓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是来这里找卡片吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人 比我更早来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 看起来还未找到卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.35,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想卡片应该就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话 请用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那里没有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.11,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我说晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我刚才也挖掘过那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会认为卡片在那里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.43,0:14:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个蔷薇就叫做红蔷薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到4点40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加活动的同学们请立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.11,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 我们将发表本次活动的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花蕾们的卡片有两张被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为令不给我提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为一定会在那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是找到白色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年级藤组 蟹名静同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～ 是静啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明用表情给过提示的 这个人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到白色卡片的地点是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委员会的公告牌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 不在蔷薇馆的第一层吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么志摩子同学为什么那时会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.16,0:15:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 是找到黄色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.56,0:15:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级菊组 田沼千里同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点是在图书馆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图书馆我也去找过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇的花蕾的卡片谁也没发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也没有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.89,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇的花蕾 红色卡片究竟在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 一起去收回卡片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 却没有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找了哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在红蔷薇根茎的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.09,0:16:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的找了这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明挖掘过同一个地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学 虽然很遗憾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有证人在场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.35,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.38,0:16:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是… 不认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就没法成为证人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都说到这种地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.42,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 这张卡片放在了比我原来埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.27,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣瓦伦丁做了一个恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样去想不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然红蔷薇的花蕾都这样说了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 能在蔷薇馆等我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.07,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.12,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.41,0:17:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特意等在这里为你送的巧克力说声谢谢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力的话这里有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是非常难吃的夹心巧克力就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.12,0:18:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 放在那里的巧克力不是佑巳的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.18,0:18:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 我已经吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.20,0:18:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为佑巳紧盯着那扇门 所以我完全以为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是非常美味的大理石花纹蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.06,0:18:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过好像是初学者做的 样子稍微有点变形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那是粉红色的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 粉红色的包装纸上印着白色蔷薇花纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.15,0:18:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蔷薇馆第一层里藏的不是白色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.65,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是志摩子同学因为犹豫着该不该交给\N白蔷薇大人而一直放在那里的巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算圣瓦伦丁的一个恶作剧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.85,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西希望你能收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道… 不会是念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念珠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我一年级的时候 好像是被姐姐完全看穿了似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.52,0:19:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我对你的心事却不怎么了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以渐渐变得没有自信了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 看起来你好像在避开我 所以稍微有点急躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那是我的误解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.27,0:19:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那是因为我想把这个送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在令大人的帮助下做出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.04,0:19:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想先对姐姐保密 才会偷偷摸摸地去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人在那里沾沾自喜地做得起劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却完全没有想到姐姐会怎么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.93,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的 姐姐讨厌情人节的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.35,0:20:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我无论如何也想将\N平常那种感谢的心情化为有形的物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.35,0:20:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过讨厌什么的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所厌烦的只是一部份学生随便地\N将送巧克力的欲望想放在我身上实现而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.31,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你为我做的东西的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会很高兴地收下它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了我不是讨厌巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一个不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 请拿这边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人请放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.64,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳你才应该…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 又是在做什么表演吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.76,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的 这叫做“吃惊的巧克力”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.82,0:21:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面混入了难吃得让人歪嘴的“不中”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才叫“吃惊”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.94,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那就是“中”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明“中”与“不中”都有一个不见了的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.00,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人会吃到“中”也算是圣瓦伦丁的…
